      <title>美国失业救济申请人数小幅上升至 225,000</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-03/us-jobless-claims-rise-slightly-to-225-000</link>
      <description><![CDATA[截至 9 月 28 日当周，首次申请失业救济人数增加 6,000 人，达到 225,000 人，这一水平与有限数量的裁员相符。迈克尔·麦基在彭博电视台报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-03/us-jobless-claims-rise-slightly-to-225-000</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 13:04:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
