    <item>
      <title>南非考虑采取措施缓解电价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/south-africa-weighs-measures-to-ease-electricity-price-increase</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非电力部长 Kgosientsho Ramokgopa 表示，南非政府正在考虑采取措施抵消拟议的电价上涨，包括推迟提高碳税的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/south-africa-weighs-measures-to-ease-electricity-price-increase</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 12:45:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
