      <title>贷款机构 Pemberton 将接管德国招聘网站 Univativ</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/lender-pemberton-set-to-take-over-german-jobs-site-univativ</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Triton Partners 准备将人才提供商 Univativ 的所有权移交给私人信贷基金 Pemberton Asset Management，后者是该公司的现有贷款人。]]></description>
